msgid "Scenario VII: Return to In the Clutches of Chaos"
msgstr "冒险VII：重返混沌魔掌"

msgid "Choose at random one of the three copies of each of the following locations: French Hill, Rivertown, Southside, South Church, Uptown, and Merchant District. Place each of these locations into play and remove the other copies from the game."
msgstr "以下每个地点，在其三张卡牌中随机选择一张：法兰西山、河岸城、南区、住宅区、南区教堂和商人区。将所选地点放置入场，并将这些地点的其他所有版本将被移出游戏。"

msgid "Each investigator begins play in Southside."
msgstr "每位调查员从南区开始游戏。"

msgid "As part of the tarot campaign reading you performed, place \"The Chariot · VII\" in the reversed position."
msgstr "你的塔罗剧本解牌是逆位的“战车·VII”。"

msgid "As part of the tarot campaign reading you performed, place \"The Chariot · VII\" in the upright position."
msgstr "你的塔罗剧本解牌是正位的“战车·VII”。"
